    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1934-08-21T04:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1934-08-21T04:00:00-05:00" n="129"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d129">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.60d31/80: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Finland</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Albright</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Helsingfors</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-08-21T11:00:00+02:00"
                            >August 21, 1934—11 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received August 21—9:25 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Following Mr. Sayre’s informal conversation Finnish authorities during recent
                    visit and my later conversation with Acting Foreign Minister I am now informed
                    by him that Finnish Government will send expert Washington about October
                    1st.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Albright</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
